
                   <p style="text-align: center">
                       <b>Title:</b> 3. For the Select binding mode step, specify the binding mode. The binding mode controls how the
endpoint is accessed using any IP address or using specific IP addresses and network interfaces.<br>
                       <b>Bounding box:</b> x1=217, y1=1242, x2=1533, y2=1910
                   </p>
